channel.title: Auto Cache Downloader Help
channel.description:
Hello, I recently downloaded Trisidiax V3 and I replaced some things in the cache and wanted to have it download my cache instead of Trisidia's. But, I've been trying for awhile now and I continuously get "Can't unzip" ect. I've replaced everything that I thought I needed to (which is like the link and name of the cache) but it still doesn't work. I really don't see the problem but here's my link to the cache if anyone could help me out. I've tried this. https://dl.dropbox.com/s/nh46rbf82h44hq9/.ProjectOPKcachev1.zip?dl=1
Along with this. https://dl.dropbox.com/s/nh46rbf82h44hq9/.ProjectOPKcachev1.zip
Thanks.
